_sText:
<font color="#2222FF">I've made a few modifications, so the map should now work on servers running Linux.  Version 2 would crash Linux servers.  T_T

The map has a new room (seen in the first screenshot) connected to the barn room.  I also added a secret passage and a secret camping spot.  The television is disabled because it caused problems.  Maybe one day I'll learn how to make a good T.V.

Comments are appreciated!!

*EDIT*
Minor update 07/06/07
-Fixed a door glitch
-Improved FPS for the new areas of the map
-Fixed the T.V. (YAY!!)
-New name is zm_complication_v4a
v4 is functional and pretty good, but doesn't have the same frame rates as v4a and the T.V. doesn't work.  Re-Download if you see fit.</font>
